A Rewrite of Matrix Algebra Subroutines
---------------------------------------

## Installation

   $ ./configure
   $ make
   $ sudo make install


## Building from GIT sources.

   Need autoconf, automake and libtool packages.

   $ libtoolize
   $ aclocal
   $ autoconf
   $ autoheader
   $ automake --add-missing
   $ ./configure
   $ make
   $ sudo make install

   Manual installation is something like following 

   $ cd src
   $ make -f makefile.test all
   $ cp .lib/libarmasd.a /usr/local/lib
   $ cp -a armas /usr/local/include
